title: Ain't Misbehavin'
script_text: Well, ain't we all just a bunch of rebels at heart? I mean it - check out the title: "Ain’t Misbehavin'"! That saucy swing is irresistible. Here’s that charmingly defiant tune by Fats Waller for you now – Ain’t Misbehavin'.
original_issue: Too aggressive/preachy - needs smooth lounge host tone
